790011560029.title: Jarrow Formulas Alpha GPC  Supports Brain Function  300mg  60 Veggie Caps
790011560029.description: Alpha GPC (L-alpha glycerylphosphorylcholine) is a phospholipid metabolite found concentrated in neuronal membranes. Alpha GPC is extremely well absorbed and crosses the blood brain barrier. Alpha GPC supports brain function and learning processes by directly increasing the synthesis and secretion of acetylcholine.* Alpha GPC supports neuronal health and improves signal transmission by serving as a precursor to membrane phospholipids.* Keep out of the reach of children.
